  description="For most Miami local service businesses, the GBP listing drives more calls than the website. Understanding why changes how you prioritize your marketing budget."
  canonical="https://thryvmarketingsolutions.com/blog/google-business-profile-vs-website/"
  ogImage="https://images.pexels.com/photos/607812/pexels-photo-607812.jpeg"
